race.comment: ATOMIC TIME (2) is unlucky to still be a maiden hitting the top-four in six of seven starts to date and strikes a very winnable contest here. Has placed around this circuit and looks the one they all have to run down. HE'S GOT GRUNT (4) is improving with racing and must be respected out of the Archibald barn. At peak fitness now and looms as the main danger. SEVILO (8) has placed over this mile journey and gets the services of Rodd in the irons. Top-three credentials. MR DEMOCRAT (6) has been just behind the placings of late and looks one for the exotics players. TAPAGAL (11) next in line from the inside alley.
